    "In order to compare the performance regarding robustness to paraphrased questions, we expand our experiments to Deepseek-R1 (DeepSeek-AI et al., 2025) and two proprietary models: Gemini 2.5 Flash Lite and Claude 3.5 Sonnet foot_3."
